    <item>
      <title>新兴市场货币因美国 CPI 数据跃升至盘中高点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/emerging-market-stocks-hit-2-year-high-amid-global-rate-cut-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[数据显示美国六月份消费者价格意外下降，巩固了人们对美联储将很快降息的预期，新兴市场货币和股票当日跃升至新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/emerging-market-stocks-hit-2-year-high-amid-global-rate-cut-bets</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 09:06:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国 CPI 数据刺激降息押注，欧洲股市上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/european-equities-edge-higher-ahead-of-key-us-inflation-data</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国通胀数据增强了对美联储9月降息的预期，欧洲股市连续第二天上涨，守住了早前的涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/european-equities-edge-higher-ahead-of-key-us-inflation-data</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 07:21:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：CPI 影响美联储 9 月降息预期，收益率下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着通货紧缩的进一步迹象增强了人们对美联储将能够很快降息的预期，全球最大的债券市场出现上涨。]]></description>
